{"tid":929901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好想對欺凌者講","createTime":"2018-12-06T02:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T15:43:42.000Z","uid":210691,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"69478b601e7510624e3293d1da5f62e4da5d49ca","tid":929901,"uid":210691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:06:50.000Z","msg":"因為本身就同佢地唔熟 而佢地又有小小背景 所以我就成為左佢地既欺凌對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 而佢地仲要扮哂大佬咁 見你同佢對望左一秒都比人打幾拳咁 而因為唔夠人打既我 只可以笑笑就算 <br />\n但有時連比人打都冇原因 只係心情唔好就打幾下咁<br />\n 我依家淨係係自己班到覺得好陌生 但同其他班既人又玩得埋咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我只可以同你地講 我屌你地老母啊 他朝君體也相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f901de79d1154c2f4669ed56afcdedaeaf579bf1","tid":929901,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"都幾無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望下就比人打<br />\nBTW FEEL 到樓主都好硬淨 <br />\n係咪下年就可以轉班啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8b5fdb85fa01739eb2487e1f55386cd9ab210d","tid":929901,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"樓豬應該係瘦撚黎<br />\n排骨仔 唔恰你恰邊個"},{"pid":"066275747c51b8593516a442f437abf29176732d","tid":929901,"uid":210691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa8b5fdb85fa01739eb2487e1f55386cd9ab210d","tid":929901,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"樓豬應該係瘦撚黎<br />\n排骨仔 唔恰你恰邊個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"我真係瘦 仲要點食都唔肥個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09dba33889516aa839267d97f3465645fa85954e","tid":929901,"uid":210691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f901de79d1154c2f4669ed56afcdedaeaf579bf1","tid":929901,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"